Measure type: [475] Restriction on entry into free circulation
Conditions:
TM816: (Taric Measure) The wood packaging material of consignments originating in China of the commodities specified in Annex I of the Commission Implementing Decision 2013/92/EU shall be subject to the plant health checks provided for in Article 3 of the abovementioned Decision.
The Frequency of plant health checks must be not less than 15% (Annex I column 3 of Decision 2013/92/EU).
